name:               cabal2nix
version:            2.14.3
x-revision: 2
synopsis:           Convert Cabal files into Nix build instructions.
description:
  Convert Cabal files into Nix build instructions. Users of Nix can install the latest
  version by running:
  .
  > nix-env -i cabal2nix
